prompts.title: Code Review Assistant
prompts.content:
Review the following code and provide feedback on:
1. Code quality and best practices
2. Potential bugs or security issues
3. Performance optimizations
4. Readability improvements

[Insert code here]
prompts.notes: Use this for comprehensive code reviews

prompts.title: Blog Post Outline Generator
prompts.content:
Create a detailed blog post outline for the topic: [TOPIC]

Include:
- Engaging title options
- Introduction hook
- 5-7 main sections with subpoints
- Key takeaways
- Call to action

Target audience: [AUDIENCE]
Tone: [TONE]

prompts.title: Photorealistic Portrait Generator
prompts.content: Create a photorealistic portrait of [DESCRIPTION], professional studio lighting, 85mm lens, shallow depth of field, high detail, 8k resolution, professional photography

prompts.title: Data Analysis Expert
prompts.content:
Analyze the following dataset and provide:

1. Summary statistics
2. Key trends and patterns
3. Outliers and anomalies
4. Actionable insights
5. Visualization recommendations

Data: [INSERT DATA]

Focus on: [SPECIFIC ASPECTS]

prompts.title: Creative Story Starter
prompts.content:
Write the opening paragraph of a [GENRE] story that:
- Immediately hooks the reader
- Establishes the setting and mood
- Introduces a compelling character or situation
- Hints at the central conflict

Theme: [THEME]
Setting: [SETTING]

prompts.title: Meeting Summary Generator
prompts.content:
Create a concise meeting summary from these notes:

[PASTE MEETING NOTES]

Include:
- Key decisions made
- Action items with owners
- Important discussion points
- Next steps and deadlines

Format as a professional memo.
prompts.notes: Saves hours of meeting follow-up time

prompts.title: Debug Assistant
prompts.content:
Help me debug this error:

Error message: [ERROR]
Code context: [CODE]
What I've tried: [ATTEMPTS]

Please:
1. Explain what's causing the error
2. Provide a step-by-step fix
3. Suggest how to prevent similar issues
4. Show the corrected code
